  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Alchemists%27_Guild\" title=\"Alchemists&#39; Guild\"><img alt=\"Pyromancer.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6b/Pyromancer.svg/50px-Pyromancer.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6b/Pyromancer.svg/75px-Pyromancer.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6b/Pyromancer.svg/100px-Pyromancer.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Wisdom</span><br />Munciter</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Alchemists%27_Guild\" title=\"Alchemists&#39; Guild\"><img alt=\"Pyromancer.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/6b/Pyromancer.svg/50px-Pyromancer.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/6b/Pyromancer.svg/75px-Pyromancer.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/6b/Pyromancer.svg/100px-Pyromancer.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Wisdom\" title=\"Wisdom\">Wisdom</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Alchemists%27_Guild\" title=\"Alchemists&#39; Guild\">Alchemists' Guild</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Crownlands\" title=\"Crownlands\">Crownlands</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Wisdom <b>Munciter</b> is a member of the <a href=\"/index.php/Alchemists%27_Guild\" title=\"Alchemists&#39; Guild\">Alchemists' Guild</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a>. He is in charge of keeping an inventory of the amount of <a href=\"/index.php/Wildfire\" title=\"Wildfire\">wildfire</a> produced by the Guild.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Munciter&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok20.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_20\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 20\">Chapter 20</a>, Tyrion V.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405005838\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.058 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.236 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 396/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10380/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4867/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 202/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 524/50000